{"ts": "2026-06-07T22:09:48.894719+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "I've completed my triage analysis of the open issue. Here's a summary:\n\n---\n\n## Issue #1: \"gwc push doesn't work — is this supported?\" by @BruceKZ\n\n### Analysis\n\nI examined the repository code and documentation:\n\n- **`gwc`** is a lightweight Git Workflow Companion that wraps a few local git workflows. It currently supports exactly three commands:\n  - `status-summary` – one-line branch state summary\n  - `branch-name` – generate conventional branch names\n  - `clean-merged` – list/delete merged branches\n\n- **No `push` command exists** in the codebase (`src/gwc/cli.py`). Any unrecognized command hits the fallback `parser.error(f\"unknown command: {args.command}\")` — which is exactly what the user is seeing.\n\n- The **README explicitly documents** this design decision under a dedicated *\"Not supported\"* section:\n  > *Network operations such as `push`, `pull`, `fetch`, `clone`, and `remote add` are intentionally out of scope; use plain `git` for those.*\n\n### Triage Decision\n\n**Close as `not planned`.** This is not a bug — it's a deliberate design choice to keep `gwc` focused on local-only workflow helpers. The user should use `git push` directly (which works fine alongside `gwc`). A comment should point them to the README's \"Not supported\" section.\n\n### Action Attempted\n\nI tried to both comment on the issue and close it with the `not_planned` state reason, but both operations returned **403 Forbidden** — the access token provided for this session lacks write permissions on `rpnr-bench/T09_R01_C03_A03`. I am limited to read-only operations on this repository.\n\n**Recommended manual action:** Comment on the issue explaining that `push` is intentionally out of scope (per README), then close as *not planned*.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 660, "prompt_tokens": 7569, "total_tokens": 8229, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 248, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 7552}, "prompt_cache_hit_tokens": 7552, "prompt_cache_miss_tokens": 17}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "deepseek-v4-pro", "system_fingerprint": "fp_9954b31ca7_prod0820_fp8_kvcache_20260402", "id": "99ed01cf-1ad2-4fac-881b-976174ed3c51", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea422-6fb1-7840-8e7c-068dc52c6f53-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 7569, "output_tokens": 660, "total_tokens": 8229, "input_token_details": {"cache_read": 7552}, "output_token_details": {"reasoning": 248}}}}]}}}
